{"tid":1392423,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[8.5 三罷] 職工盟稱暫有26個工會響應下周一罷工行動","createTime":"2019-07-31T17:37:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T06:59:35.000Z","uid":195252,"like":36,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"d52fb42a2d7256ce65d008233f22dcd4ac36d752","tid":1392423,"uid":195252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T17:37:08.000Z","msg":"source:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1471545-20190731.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1471545-20190731.htm&d=puaUx2dgpXXsrsLU9noyGDKIKeATNbIGZROv3ilSK6E%3D&h=333dc97f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1471545-20190731.htm&h=f171b822\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1471545-20190731.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n&lt;職工盟稱暫有26個工會響應下周一罷工行動&gt;<br />\n<br />\n職工盟主席吳敏兒說，現時有26個工會表示會響應下星期一的罷工行動，預料對公私營機構運作將造成不便。<br />\n<br />\n吳敏兒出席一個電台節目後表示，不合作運動已擴展至不同層面，如果政府繼續不回應，第3次罷工將會升級行動。<br />\n<br />\n她表示，下星期一的罷工是不上班的罷工，參與的僱員需通知僱主，《基本法》賦予員工享有罷工權利，只要僱員有以口頭或書面通知僱主，僱主在罷工後不能留難僱員。<br />\n<br />\n吳敏兒說，僱主大多只會扣減罷工僱員的一日薪金，如果僱員在罷工後，懷疑受到不合理的對待，可通知工會。"},{"pid":"784c4b023237f373c40adefd0d3f44775eeb477f","tid":1392423,"uid":195252,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T17:37:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QYFZ42e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQYFZ42e.jpg&h=dd3e50d3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"be3f5e29dcc79ab0084310975f29686d6b94a5aa","tid":1392423,"uid":195252,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T17:38:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aonasfH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaonasfH.png&h=883434f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yFB22O3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyFB22O3.png&h=bb43af4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/66EHino.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F66EHino.png&h=a8787ee7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"751542d2d793a4203340816846576ee1afe7e275","tid":1392423,"uid":290385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T17:38:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d959c0f7a879b62f66dcc76324c6e0423618cf5f","tid":1392423,"uid":195252,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T17:42:40.000Z","msg":"我係香港人，我願意罷工"},{"pid":"28836c516d733c41ef0de28962867eb73513c9eb","tid":1392423,"uid":216789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T17:48:28.000Z","msg":"<strong>慎防黑惡勢力蔓延禍港，提防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團</strong><br />\n<br />\n鑒於近日有無辜香港市民慘遭黑勢力人仕襲擊，現懇切呼籲各香港市民不論男女，請慎防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團，保障自身安全，萬事小心，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">切忌助長黑惡勢力氣焰</span></strong>"},{"pid":"93052b2f2fdec640cd7ffba8602108ad532bbf4e","tid":1392423,"uid":283912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T17:55:38.000Z","msg":"呢個要推阿屌!強心針!"},{"pid":"edf688960c2a016605586f554580c75bf7666194","tid":1392423,"uid":195252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T17:56:21.000Z","msg":"我係香港人，我願意罷工"},{"pid":"d940955ee73994e042dc22e949b0e049e5cde368","tid":1392423,"uid":12180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T18:09:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2b70c9266f692c1bf60b7000a36c91f80f544aa2","tid":1392423,"uid":195252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T18:44:28.000Z","msg":"我係香港人，我願意罷工"},{"pid":"48a0a4f3c0f49d505ac97b7cf9d10f02e9782146","tid":1392423,"uid":62776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T18:49:05.000Z","msg":"支持三罷"},{"pid":"bd7db389b0ae14791a997cf4518930d17788d477","tid":1392423,"uid":158404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T18:51:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"84d11062e144b2613d6a662b568d52cc5